             was indicted for <rs id="t18291029-83-off446" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-83-off446" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-83-off446" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-83-cd447" type="crimeDate">5th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-83-off446 t18291029-83-cd447"></join>, 10 shirts, value 40s.; 19 shirt collars, value 15s.; 1 basket, value 6d., and 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18291029-83-victim688" type="victimName">
                        Sarah 
                        Thornhill
                     <interp inst="t18291029-83-victim688" type="surname" value="Thornhill"></interp>
